{
  "info": {
    "name": "AIAA Backend (prod)",
    "_postman_id": "aiaa-backend-prod-0001",
    "description": "AI Academy Asia backend API — points at https://api.ai-academy.asia.\n\nUsage:\n1. Run **Auth › Login** first — it auto-saves access_token + refresh_token to collection variables.\n2. All protected requests inherit `Bearer {{access_token}}`.\n3. Create requests (course/student/teacher) auto-save their id to a variable used by the follow-up requests.\n4. When the access token expires (1h), run **Auth › Refresh** to rotate it.\n\nRoles: super_admin (all), content_marketing (course:edit), sales_enrollment (student:manage/teacher:manage), finance.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{access_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "https://api.ai-academy.asia" },
    { "key": "access_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "refresh_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "course_slug", "value": "" },
    { "key": "student_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "teacher_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "classroom_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "cohort_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', j.access_token);",
                  "if (j.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', j.refresh_token);",
                  "console.log('must_change_password =', j.must_change_password);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "login"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ai-academy.asia\",\n  \"password\": \"CHANGE_ME\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "var j = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (j.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', j.access_token);",
                  "if (j.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', j.refresh_token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "refresh"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "me"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/change-password", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "change-password"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"current_password\": \"CHANGE_ME\",\n  \"new_password\": \"NewStrongPass123\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout (this device)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "logout"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout all",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/logout-all", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "logout-all"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
